Package com.intel.fightclub.dialog.coach.commentary

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommentaryAdapter
    This class takes a Comment from the coach engine and unflattens complex objects, adapting to a format expected by CUI.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CommentaryItem
    Items that are included in commentary events.
    DialogCommentCode
    Types of comments emitted by the engine, mapped into Dialog codes.
    DialogCommentDescriptor
    Implements descriptors for comment codes sent by PLTech.
    DialogCommentTopic
    This enum lists all topic values from Coach Engine, and provides the names expected by DialogueEngine.
    DialogComplianceLevel  
    DialogDelta  
    DialogOutOfZoneReason
    Enum describing reason why a user goes out of zone
    DialogPaceMeasure  
    DialogPerformanceType
    Defines supported performance types for utterance generation.
    DialogProgramType
    Defines program type codes used in utterance generation.
    DialogZoneMetric
    This enum lists all zone metrics supported by the Coach Engine, and maps them to codes expected by Dialog Engine.
    GlobalDescriptor
    Global descriptors that can be added to commentary generation in this domain.
    NonArdaUtteranceId
    Unlike those in DialogCommentCode, this enumeration defines utterance ids available in the commentary databases that do not relate to ARDA comment codes, i.e. codes that exist in the database and are not part of the coaching engine's commentary.
    VolumeComplianceDescriptorSet
    Consolidates sets of descriptors used for flattening VolumeCompliance instances.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ArdaCommentaryAdapterException
    Exception thrown when DB is malformed somehow.
